{"tid":483567,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港學生四川實習 嘆當地不說普通話難溝通","createTime":"2017-11-29T08:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T03:38:47.000Z","uid":144372,"like":3,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8048ba487b892ad61bc7dd246ab84d748a949a5b","tid":483567,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:35:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2016/01/25/CH1601250034.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2016%2F01%2F25%2FCH1601250034.htm&d=%2BajzBnAb0PlQEQmw%2Fg88usmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=f6d37c2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2016/01/25/CH1601250034.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港學生曾嘉儀曾擔任過香港赴川實習小組的組長，當初所實習的單位是興業銀行。「因為四川的人日常是用四川話來溝通，很少說普通話，加上我的普通話也不太標準，很多時候雙方遇到溝通障礙，本來性格沉穩的我有些手足無措。」<br />\n曾嘉儀笑說，「但是我會盡我所能聆聽客人的要求，而共事的前輩們也會及時幫助，更有客戶會不斷鼓勵我。感謝他們給了我如此溫暖的實習體驗，讓我學到了不少知識，亦希望將來嘗試在銀行方面發展。」"},{"pid":"866243cc6b4b36a4c650d778afd4cf33c77999b6","tid":483567,"uid":36806,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"香港學生：我呀媽是女人"},{"pid":"cec1ce16f53715825222238850f968dc00245778","tid":483567,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":27,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母迫四川人講廣東話<br />\n就好似迫香港人講廣東話咁自以為是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"18805e26b5f5725a9927d53fa0ef01335265def9","tid":483567,"uid":47359,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母迫四川人講廣東話<br />\n就好似迫香港人講廣東話咁自以為是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquo